name: The two Levels
description:
I have used the unity game engine.

 How to play: WASD to move, up arrow key to climb walls.  HINTS: At the second level at the invisible wall press a Key to go through . 

This is my first finished game and my first game jam and i had a lot of fun! 

Yes, the controls are inversed on purpose.

Let's see what time you get  :)
